com.google.zxing.client.result
Class ResultParser

java.lang.Object
  com.google.zxing.client.result.ResultParser
Direct Known Subclasses:
ISBNResultParser
public abstract class ResultParser
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract class representing the result of decoding a barcode, as more than a String -- as some type of structured data. This might be a subclass which represents a URL, or an e-mail address. parseResult(com.google.zxing.Result) will turn a raw decoded string into the most appropriate type of structured representation.

Thanks to Jeff Griffin for proposing rewrite of these classes that relies less on exception-based mechanisms during parsing.

Author:
Sean Owen
